        "C": "all terms positive",
        "D": "ratio less than 1 always"
      },
      "correct": "B",
      "explanation": "Need decreasing positive b_n and lim b_n=0.",
      "notesSection": "10.4 - Alternating Series Test",
      "notesSnippet": "Check monotonic decrease and limit zero.",
